### Зарегистрироваться
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "username",
  "passwordHash": "passsssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssswordHash",
  "publicKey": "publicKeypublicKeypublicKeypublicKeypublicKeypublicKeypublicKeypublicKey",
  "encryptedPrivateKey": "privateKeyprivateKeyprivateKeyprivateKeyprivateKeyprivateKeyprivateKey"
}

###
